script.name: plugin.tradesys.cmd.route.menu
script.description: Trade Sys MK3: Trade Route Command (Menu)
script.sourceplaintext:
$DATA = get global variable: name='trade.route.data' $page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.guilds'
if $a.event == [MEvent.Start] @ $tRoutes = $a.obj -> call script plugin.tradesys.getroutes : Range=5 $DATA = table alloc $DATA['sort'] = 'ware' $DATA['sort.rev'] = [FALSE] $DATA['range'] = 5 $DATA['routes'] = $tRoutes set global variable: name='trade.route.data' value=$DATA gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input
else if $a.event == [MEvent.TradeBarCh] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'buy.at' $a.obj ->set local variable: name='mtc.buy.val' value=$value $ware = $DATA['ware'] gosub sub.BuyMenu return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Search] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $value = $a.data[1] if $menu.id == 'trade.route.menu' $DATA['search'] = $value gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Update] $menu.id = $a.data[0] if $menu.id == 'buy.at' $ware = $DATA['ware'] gosub sub.BuyMenu return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Hotkey] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'trade.route.menu' if $selection == 'info' $input = create input: id='info' encyclopedia page, ware=$value return $input end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Context] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'trade.route.menu' if $value == 'info' $input = create input: id='info' encyclopedia page, ware=$selection return $input else if $value == 'buy.at' $ware = $selection $route = $DATA['routes'][$ware] $value = $route[5] $a.obj ->set local variable: name='mtc.buy.val' value=$value $DATA['ware'] = $ware gosub sub.BuyMenu return $input else if $value == 'dock.at' $tRoutes = $DATA['routes'] if $tRoutes $route = $tRoutes[$selection] if $route $destination = $route[1] START $a.obj -> delayed command COMMAND_DOCKAT : arg1=$destination, arg2=null, arg3=null, arg4=null $speak = create new array, arguments=[Page.MiscVoice], 131, [Page.MiscVoice], 1264, null START speak array: $speak prio=50 $ret = create menu return to previous menu: value=[TRUE] return $ret end end end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.HeadingClick] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'trade.route.menu' if $selection == 'main.heading' $sortBy = $DATA['sort'] if $value < 200 $DATA['sort'] = 'ware' else if $value < 430 $DATA['sort'] = 'source' else if $value < 630 $DATA['sort'] = 'dest' else if $value < 690 $DATA['sort'] = 'amt' else if $value < 760 $DATA['sort'] = 'ship' else $DATA['sort'] = 'profit' end $value = $DATA['sort'] if $sortBy == $value if $DATA['sort.rev'] $DATA['sort.rev'] = [FALSE] else $DATA['sort.rev'] = [TRUE] end else $DATA['sort.rev'] = [FALSE] end end gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Switch] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'trade.route.menu' if $selection == 'range' $DATA['range'] = $value @ $tRoutes = $a.obj -> call script plugin.tradesys.getroutes : Range=$value $DATA['routes'] = $tRoutes end gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Returned] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $value if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $value.array = $value $value = $value[0] end
if $menu.id == 'trade.route.menu' if $selection == 'buy.at' $ware = $value $value = $value.array[1] $route = $DATA['routes'][$ware] $destination = $route[1] $ret = create new array, arguments=$ware, $destination, null, null, null START $a.obj -> delayed command COMMAND_MANUAL_TRADE_BUY : arg1=$ret, arg2=$value, arg3=null, arg4=null $speak = create new array, arguments=[Page.MiscVoice], 131, [Page.MiscVoice], 1264, null START speak array: $speak prio=50 $ret = create menu return to previous menu: value=[TRUE] return $ret end end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Finished] $a.obj ->set local variable: name='mtc.buy.val' value=null set global variable: name='trade.route.data' value=null end
* ===================================== return null
* ===================================== * =====================================
* ===================================== sub.BuyMenu: $route = $DATA['routes'][$ware] $destination = $route[1]
$menu = create custom menu array $heading = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=9306 $default = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='mtc.buy.val' @ = [THIS] -> call script !lib.menu.tradebar.trade : Ship=$a.obj Station=$destination Product=$ware Menu Array=$menu Current Value=$default Selling?=[FALSE] Heading=$heading set menu option: $menu, icon=7 set menu option: $menu, maximum menu height=7 lines $title = read text: page=6001 id=9 $text = read text: page=6001 id=7 $input = create input: id='buy.at', dynamic menu=$menu, title=$title, description=$text, callback=[Callback.TradeBarCh], update=1000ms endsub
* ===================================== sub.BuildMenu: $menu = create custom menu array
$tRoutes = $DATA['routes']
$aValues = array alloc: size=10 $i = size of array $aValues while $i dec $i = $aValues[$i] = $i end $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3207 $default = $DATA['range'] add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, value array=$aValues, default=$default, return id='range', width=100 allowtabs=[FALSE]
$text.cols = array alloc: size=6 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3201 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3202 $text = create custom menu column string, position=200 length=230 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[1] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3203 $text = create custom menu column string, position=430 length=230 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[2] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3204 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-170 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[3] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3205 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-100 length=70 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[4] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3206 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[5] = $text add clickable heading: menu=$menu, text=$text.cols, id='main.heading', allow empty=[FALSE]
$drawn = [FALSE] if $tRoutes if size of table $tRoutes $sort.data = table alloc $ware = get next key: table=$tRoutes key=null $sortBy = $DATA['sort'] while $ware $source = $tRoutes[$ware][1] $destination = $tRoutes[$ware][2] if $sortBy == 'ware' $value = $ware else if $sortBy == 'source' $value = $source -> get name else if $sortBy == 'dest' $value = $destination -> get name else if $sortBy == 'amt' $source.got = $source -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $dest.free = $destination -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $value = get minimum, $source.got, $dest.free, null, null, null else if $sortBy == 'ship' $source.got = $source -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $dest.free = $destination -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $ship.free = $a.obj -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $value = get minimum, $source.got, $dest.free, $ship.free, null, null else if $sortBy == 'profit' $source.got = $source -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $dest.free = $destination -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $ship.free = $a.obj -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $ship.qty = get minimum, $source.got, $dest.free, $ship.free, null, null $source.price = $source -> get price of ware $ware $dest.price = $destination -> get price of ware $ware $price.diff = $dest.price - $source.price $value = $ship.qty * $price.diff else $value = $ware end $sort.data[$ware] = $value $ware = get next key: table=$tRoutes key=$ware end
$aSorted = sort table keys by value: table=$sort.data
do if $DATA['sort.rev'] $aSorted = reverse array $aSorted $search.str = $DATA['search']
$size = size of array $aSorted $i = 0 while $i < $size $ware = $aSorted[$i] set discovered status: type=$ware status=[TRUE] inc $i =
if $search.str if get length of string $search.str $text = sprintf: fmt='%s', $ware, null, null, null, null skip if case insensitive string match, is $search.str in $text continue end end
$route = $tRoutes[$ware]
$source = $route[1] $destination = $route[2]
$side.menu = create custom menu array set menu option: $side.menu, icon=29 set menu option: $side.menu, set title text=$ware $text = get volume of ware $ware $text = convert number $text to string $text = create text for custom menu, left=[Text.Volume], right=$text add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text $text = get transport class of ware $ware $text = create text for custom menu, left=[Text.TC], right=$text add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text set menu line option: $menu, side menu=$side.menu $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3202 add info line heading to menu: $side.menu, heading=$read.text $text = $source -> get name add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text $text = $source -> get sector add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text $source.price = $source -> get price of ware $ware $text = convert number $source.price to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s %s', $text, [Text.Credits], null, null, null add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text $amt = $source -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $max = $source -> get max amount of ware $ware that can be stored in cargo bay $percent = fixed multiply and divide: $amt * 100 / $max $text.cols = array alloc: size=2 $text = create custom menu string progress: width=100 progress=$percent% $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[0] = $text $text = convert number $amt to string $text2 = convert number $max to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s / %s', $text, $text2, null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=10 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text.cols $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3203 add info line heading to menu: $side.menu, heading=$read.text $text = $destination -> get name add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text $text = $destination -> get sector add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text $dest.price = $destination -> get price of ware $ware $text = convert number $dest.price to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s %s', $text, [Text.Credits], null, null, null add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text $amt = $destination -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $max = $destination -> get max amount of ware $ware that can be stored in cargo bay $percent = fixed multiply and divide: $amt * 100 / $max $text.cols = array alloc: size=2 $text = create custom menu string progress: width=100 progress=$percent% $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[0] = $text $text = convert number $amt to string $text2 = convert number $max to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s / %s', $text, $text2, null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=10 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text add custom menu info line to array $side.menu: text=$text.cols
$text.cols = array alloc: size=8 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$ware $text.cols[0] = $text $text = $source ->create custom menu string object icon $text = create custom menu column string, position=200 length=10 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text $text = $source -> get name $text = create custom menu column string, position=210 length=220 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text $text = $destination ->create custom menu string object icon $text = create custom menu column string, position=430 length=10 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[3] = $text $text = $destination -> get name $text = create custom menu column string, position=440 length=220 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[4] = $text $source.got = $source -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $dest.free = $destination -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $ware.qty = get minimum, $source.got, $dest.free, null, null, null $text = convert number $ware.qty to string $text = create custom menu column string, position=-170 length=70 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[5] = $text
$ship.free = $a.obj -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $ship.qty = get minimum, $ship.free, $ware.qty, null, null, null
$text = convert number $ship.qty to string $text = create custom menu column string, position=-100 length=70 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[6] = $text
$source.price = $source -> get price of ware $ware $dest.price = $destination -> get price of ware $ware $price.diff = $dest.price - $source.price
$value = $ship.qty * $price.diff $text = convert number $value to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s %s', $text, [Text.Credits], null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[7] = $text
$context = create context menu $ret = create menu return value: context menu, id=$ware, menu=$context, dynamic=[FALSE] $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=812 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=29, returnvalue='info', hotkey=[Key.Identity], disabled=[FALSE] add context menu separator: menu=$context $read.text = read text: page=[Page.QMenus] id=140203 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=21, returnvalue='dock.at', hotkey=537, disabled=[FALSE] $read.text = read text: page=[Page.QMenus] id=140204 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=5, returnvalue='buy.at', hotkey=536, disabled=[FALSE] add context menu global info line: menu=$context, name='Ware', value=$ware
add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.cols returnvalue=$ret $drawn = [TRUE] end end end
if not $drawn $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text end
set menu option: $menu, remove main header=[TRUE] set menu option: $menu, icon=3 set menu option: $menu, widthtype=[MenuWidth.Huge] set menu option: $menu, global hotkey=[Key.Identity], id='info' set menu option: $menu, default value select='range' set menu option: $menu, allow searching=[TRUE]
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3200 $input = create input: id='trade.route.menu' menu=$menu title=$read.text description=$a.obj callback=[Callback.Switch]
endsub return null
